query:
SELECT a.id as assetId, a.name, a.address, a.projectId, 
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM assessments WHERE assetId = a.id) as assessmentCount,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM deficiencies WHERE projectId = a.projectId) as projectDeficiencyCount
FROM assets a 
WHERE a.name LIKE '%Comox%' OR a.address LIKE '%Comox%';
